{"tid":590664,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"頸椎病睇脊柱神經科定中醫","createTime":"2018-03-13T00:00:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-20T05:30:19.000Z","uid":116774,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"aebaf292980022f0689f17c1c9733788e1ebcd54","tid":590664,"uid":116774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T00:00:45.000Z","msg":"唔知有無人會禁入黎睇呢 :(<br />\n<br />\n我有脊柱側彎，頸有前傾，有移位。但幾勁唔知。<br />\n近幾年有心悸問題。<br />\n最近耳鳴明顯左，頭暈。近幾日左手手痺。。。<br />\n本身有睇開中醫(普通中醫)，但係都無咩用。<br />\n<br />\n想問下頸椎病睇識骨科頸椎中醫還是睇脊柱神經科/脊醫好？"},{"pid":"ca3d6fe440c3ec340ba233e77c78d4661c81f31f","tid":590664,"uid":57835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T00:16:19.000Z","msg":"中醫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7194466a486c7aefad7c1046229d9c658c1b300b","tid":590664,"uid":33125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T00:17:33.000Z","msg":"中大中醫診所骨傷科"},{"pid":"f7431068a4f7b7f71fa40faaa2a7589ed75b5421","tid":590664,"uid":174084,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"aebaf292980022f0689f17c1c9733788e1ebcd54","tid":590664,"uid":116774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T00:00:45.000Z","msg":"唔知有無人會禁入黎睇呢 :(<br />\n<br />\n我有脊柱側彎，頸有前傾，有移位。但幾勁唔知。<br />\n近幾年有心悸問題。<br />\n最近耳鳴明顯左，頭暈。近幾日左手手痺。。。<br />\n本身有睇開中醫(普通中醫)，但係都無咩用。<br />\n<br />\n想問下頸椎病睇識骨科頸椎中醫還是睇脊柱神經科/脊醫好？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T00:49:15.000Z","msg":"本身有睇開中醫(普通中醫)，但係都無咩用 =&gt; 脊醫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n中醫呃9人就有人<br />\n有用既話班強國人就唔會過來睇醫生<br />\n之前香港讀中醫果班人乞食咁濟<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E8%84%8A%E9%AA%A8%E7%A5%9E%E7%B6%93%E9%86%AB%E5%AD%B8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E8%2584%258A%25E9%25AA%25A8%25E7%25A5%259E%25E7%25B6%2593%25E9%2586%25AB%25E5%25AD%25B8&d=LOaIFZsR68d32QMx6awQTTPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=c3f2ef76\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E8%84%8A%E9%AA%A8%E7%A5%9E%E7%B6%93%E9%86%AB%E5%AD%B8</a><br />\n<br />\n&quot;脊科醫學是一個獨立的醫療體系，脊醫是第一線 醫療人員，跟西醫、牙醫同享獨立而平衡的地位，脊科醫學並非西醫中的分科，不需經任何轉介，可直接為病人診治。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n呢個唔錯<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.adio.hk/index.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.adio.hk%2Findex.aspx&d=LOaIFZsR68d32QMx6awQTTPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=89550fc8\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.adio.hk/index.aspx</a>"},{"pid":"aa746604acfe8db9b48e109fb098b5e3d80d87ee","tid":590664,"uid":130901,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T00:51:11.000Z","msg":"非常認真，未必關頸脊事，早排生過神經瘤做完手術，都係頸痛耳鳴，建議睇下耳鼻喉科照下磁力共振，唔好單睇脊椎<br />\n<br />\n上網search聽神經瘤"},{"pid":"269b50183ec2656cf1d9b6f872bd5e42e2e5c767","tid":590664,"uid":34109,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T00:52:52.000Z","msg":"其實脊醫唔係醫生"},{"pid":"4cb4108bf4dbf8bfae3a1b27d495e5cb2109a7ae","tid":590664,"uid":174084,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"269b50183ec2656cf1d9b6f872bd5e42e2e5c767","tid":590664,"uid":34109,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T00:52:52.000Z","msg":"其實脊醫唔係醫生"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T00:56:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap428!zh-Hant-HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.elegislation.gov.hk%2Fhk%2Fcap428%21zh-Hant-HK&d=LOaIFZsR68d32QMx6awQTTPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=7ae174e8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap428!zh-Hant-HK</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.blis.gov.hk/blis_pdf.nsf/CurAllChinDoc/BB885695AF3D74E6482575EF000710E8?OpenDocument\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.blis.gov.hk%2Fblis_pdf.nsf%2FCurAllChinDoc%2FBB885695AF3D74E6482575EF000710E8%3FOpenDocument&d=LOaIFZsR68d32QMx6awQTTPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=0fed8c76\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.blis.gov.hk/blis_pdf.nsf/CurAllChinDoc/BB885695AF3D74E6482575EF000710E8?OpenDocument</a><br />\n<br />\n脊醫註冊條例<br />\n<br />\n醫生(普通科)係西醫<br />\n脊醫就係脊醫<br />\n<br />\n請多讀一點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f40905dff1bf3d41720c6c84d719dfb76ea0c15d","tid":590664,"uid":88879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aebaf292980022f0689f17c1c9733788e1ebcd54","tid":590664,"uid":116774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T00:00:45.000Z","msg":"唔知有無人會禁入黎睇呢 :(<br />\n<br />\n我有脊柱側彎，頸有前傾，有移位。但幾勁唔知。<br />\n近幾年有心悸問題。<br />\n最近耳鳴明顯左，頭暈。近幾日左手手痺。。。<br />\n本身有睇開中醫(普通中醫)，但係都無咩用。<br />\n<br />\n想問下頸椎病睇識骨科頸椎中醫還是睇脊柱神經科/脊醫好？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T00:59:09.000Z","msg":"你有幾肯定啲症狀同側彎有關係？有冇做檢查之類？症狀幾耐，越耐既乜醫都難攪<br />\n<br />\n中醫：幫你解決到麻痺同心悸等症狀，但唔會幫你變直<br />\n骨傷中醫（唔係跌打）：好彩既可以變返正<br />\n脊醫：理論上可解決問題<br />\n神經科：手術for sure,不過問題可能會反覆<br />\n<br />\n最緊要係自己有冇再好好愛錫條頸，唔係都晒醫藥費"},{"pid":"1b86e37687902ca5205c8fef27b85b7c197d40bc","tid":590664,"uid":174084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aa746604acfe8db9b48e109fb098b5e3d80d87ee","tid":590664,"uid":130901,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T00:51:11.000Z","msg":"非常認真，未必關頸脊事，早排生過神經瘤做完手術，都係頸痛耳鳴，建議睇下耳鼻喉科照下磁力共振，唔好單睇脊椎<br />\n<br />\n上網search聽神經瘤"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T01:01:05.000Z","msg":"脊柱側彎，頸有前傾，有移位。 =&gt; 脊柱同頸壓住神經線也有可能會引起樓主的病症<br />\n<br />\n無論耳鼻喉科或任何專科<br />\n不過實際情況要先照左片先知<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n快D去睇醫生"},{"pid":"3ca206a7822199ecc85597e4f006e8b5aae4436b","tid":590664,"uid":130901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1b86e37687902ca5205c8fef27b85b7c197d40bc","tid":590664,"uid":174084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aa746604acfe8db9b48e109fb098b5e3d80d87ee","tid":590664,"uid":130901,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T00:51:11.000Z","msg":"非常認真，未必關頸脊事，早排生過神經瘤做完手術，都係頸痛耳鳴，建議睇下耳鼻喉科照下磁力共振，唔好單睇脊椎<br />\n<br />\n上網search聽神經瘤"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"