>\n<br />\n我有脊柱側彎，頸有前傾，有移位。但幾勁唔知。<br />\n近幾年有心悸問題。<br />\n最近耳鳴明顯左，頭暈。近幾日左手手痺。。。<br />\n本身有睇開中醫(普通中醫)，但係都無咩用。<br />\n<br />\n想問下頸椎病睇識骨科頸椎中醫還是睇脊柱神經科/脊醫好？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n自己search下海豚操"},{"pid":"149db2167a845630157da6785271f3ace88ec1a9","tid":590664,"uid":40387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T02:16:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/FYpaW6tF15A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FFYpaW6tF15A&d=LOaIFZsR68d32QMx6awQTTPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=aa6b08c7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/FYpaW6tF15A</a>"},{"pid":"0fbcea475204c445653f84cfd15343b3b28c8f4a","tid":590664,"uid":125488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f7431068a4f7b7f71fa40faaa2a7589ed75b5421","tid":590664,"uid":174084,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"aebaf292980022f0689f17c1c9733788e1ebcd54","tid":590664,"uid":116774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T00:00:45.000Z","msg":"唔知有無人會禁入黎睇呢 :(<br />\n<br />\n我有脊柱側彎，頸有前傾，有移位。但幾勁唔知。<br />\n近幾年有心悸問題。<br />\n最近耳鳴明顯左，頭暈。近幾日左手手痺。。。<br />\n本身有睇開中醫(普通中醫)，但係都無咩用。<br />\n<br />\n想問下頸椎病睇識骨科頸椎中醫還是睇脊柱神經科/脊醫好？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T00:49:15.000Z","msg":"本身有睇開中醫(普通中醫)，但係都無咩用 =&gt; 脊醫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n中醫呃9人就有人<br />\n有用既話班強國人就唔會過來睇醫生<br />\n之前香港讀中醫果班人乞食咁濟<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E8%84%8A%E9%AA%A8%E7%A5%9E%E7%B6%93%E9%86%AB%E5%AD%B8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E8%2584%258A%25E9%25AA%25A8%25E7%25A5%259E%25E7%25B6%2593%25E9%2586%25AB%25E5%25AD%25B8&d=LOaIFZsR68d32QMx6awQTTPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=c3f2ef76\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E8%84%8A%E9%AA%A8%E7%A5%9E%E7%B6%93%E9%86%AB%E5%AD%B8</a><br />\n<br />\n&quot;脊科醫學是一個獨立的醫療體系，脊醫是第一線 醫療人員，跟西醫、牙醫同享獨立而平衡的地位，脊科醫學並非西醫中的分科，不需經任何轉介，可直接為病人診治。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n呢個唔錯<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.adio.hk/index.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.adio.hk%2Findex.aspx&d=LOaIFZsR68d32QMx6awQTTPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=89550fc8\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.adio.hk/index.aspx</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T02:19:00.000Z","msg":"中醫聽講人工唔係唔錯咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa8d99d413445229cb404dcd25a2ab43ec752b01","tid":590664,"uid":131963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"149db2167a845630157da6785271f3ace88ec1a9","tid":590664,"uid":40387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T02:16:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/FYpaW6tF15A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FFYpaW6tF15A&d=LOaIFZsR68d32QMx6awQTTPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=aa6b08c7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/FYpaW6tF15A</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T02:20:08.000Z","msg":"平時有無做開運動？<br />\n可以做下簡單既瑜伽."},{"pid":"32a8e71d10207a74bf0f3bc9289ad00cc6ef6a8f","tid":590664,"uid":116774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T13:39:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"https://youtu.be/FYpaW6tF15A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FFYpaW6tF15A&d=LOaIFZsR68d32QMx6awQTTPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=aa6b08c7\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/FYpaW6tF15A</a></blockquote>平時有無做開運動？<br />\n可以做下簡單既瑜伽.</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n平時唔做運動<br />\n有諗過做yoga，但係做yoga會唔會令到情況惡化？"},{"pid":"8a1af4ef20d171596b72f52a789a6d64f2b9ba9a","tid":590664,"uid":131963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"32a8e71d10207a74bf0f3bc9289ad00cc6ef6a8f","tid":590664,"uid":116774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T13:39:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"https://youtu.be/FYpaW6tF15A\" data-sr-url=\"ht